Project:  CASE, SUM, GROUP BY and ORDER all applied on identity data
Created by: Mohamed Raghe
**************************************
UPDATES: 
@case statement with SUM, GROUP BY and ORDER BY

		SELECT group_description, sum(round(fte_sum, 0)) headcounts,
	case 
	    when sum(fte_sum)< 5000 then "small_sized_group" 
	    when sum(fte_sum) BETWEEN 5001 and 10000 then "middle_sized_group" 
	    else "big_sized_group"  
	    end as Company_size
	from prd_product_law_ethics.hr_employee_aggregates 
	GROUP BY group_description
	ORDER BY headcounts desc
